one_reviews_text: I got more play time out of the free version on my iPhone.  This cost $.99 and gives very little play time and then an ad.  Which btw when you try to use their option to see the "next" product, my Trend Micro virus scanner caught and deleted the inmind.exe because it saw malware like activity.
The game lasts about 5 minutes, waste of 79p....  only really worth 10p if you ask me.
A great use of just using the headset. Good for kids
